thread.title: TFI Friday

author: Fiona Flynn
title: TFI Friday
text: It's back! The hugely popular nineties chat show returns for a brand new series following on from the success of the 20th anniversary special over the summer. Chris Evans will of course be at the helm, and similar to The Graham Norton Show tonight, he also has a notable Irish lineup in store for us with both U2 and actress Saoirse Ronan on the bill. As well as that, Take That will be stopping by for a song while Steve Coogan and Slaves also join Chris. Will it manage to create that feeling of utter madness the original incarnation had? Here's hoping.
